Name: Aala Sharfi
Bio: Aala is a multi-disciplinary designer specialising in branding and publication design. Aala's strengths lie in identity design, digital and print design.

Name: Peter Smith
Bio: Pete is a software consultant, speaker & writer.

Name: Sam Elamin
Bio: Sam has over 15 years experience as a developer and has worked in some of the world's largest companies such as Sony Playstation, Discovery Communications and JustEat. He was also the previous CEO of Kylin Network

Name: Sophie McKinnon
Bio: Sophie carefully crafted Zappy from the ground up, along with Jennifer to make sure the User Interfaces are not only appealing to the eye, but also user-friendly. And boy did she did a killer job.

Name: Tom Brennan
Bio: Tom Brennan is a programmer with over a decade of experience working with DBMS, web development, and automation. He believes decentralization represents the stirrings of world government that will lead humanity closer to a Star Trek future.

Name: Troy Davis
Bio: Troy joined the team in 2020 to help us with the development of our app and dashboard. This amazingly talented young man made Zappy a reality in no-time. Troy is now our Lead Developer and makes sure Zappy uses the latest technology.
